Title: Witness
Plot: Erin Kendall (guest star Danica McKellar) claims to have seen a murder of a sailor in an apartment across from hers. Gibbs assigns the case to McGee who believes that he can resolve it himself. However, due to the lack of physical evidence, McGee turns to the team to help him...
GuestStars: Jack McGee, Danica McKellar, Tina Lifford, Conor Dubin, Brian Dietzen, Colleen Porch, Christopher Stapleton
